Class Location

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.DataResource
      • sep.gaia.resources.locationsearch.Location
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Location
extends DataResource
    Bean class to save the name, the region and the position (i.e. the longitude and latitude) of a location to be searched for.
